Author: incompetentpos
Text: I'm assuming that your priority is your health, so I'd advise you to be as honest as you can be. It's unlikely that they'll put you in an inpatient program.

Author: jcsxx
Text: They usually don’t put people in inpatient unless they’re medically unstable so you’ll probably be referred to a therapist and dietician/nutritionist or maybe they’ll give you options for an outpatient program?
